### include=reviews -> reviewCount, @EntityGraph (1 query, no N+1)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/products?include=reviews

### include=images -> thumbnailUrl, @EntityGraph (1 query, no N+1)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/products?include=images

### include both (query params on separate lines - avoids IntelliJ inline-& bug)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/products
        ?include=reviews
        &include=images

### no include -> id + name only
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/products

### unknown include -> ignored, plain list (no validation currently)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/products?include=xyz
